---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact Us - Schedule Strategic Session
description: Schedule a confidential strategic consultation with Louis & Rob. Discuss your enterprise growth objectives. Phone (555) 123-4567 or email hello@seaena.com
breadcrumbs:
  - name: Contact
    url: /contact/
---


<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ContactPage",
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "{{ site.name }}",
    "contactPoint": {
      "@type": "ContactPoint",
      "telephone": "{{ site.phone }}",
      "contactType": "Customer Service",
      "email": "{{ site.email }}",
      "availableLanguage": "English"
    }
  }
}
</script>



<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Schedule Strategic Session</h1>
      <p class="hero-subheading">Confidential consultation with Louis & Rob to discuss your enterprise growth objectives</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2">
      <!-- Contact Form -->
      <div>
        <h2>Get Started</h2>
        <p>Complete this form to schedule a 30-minute strategic consultation. We'll discuss your business objectives, challenges, and how Seaena can help.</p>

        <form class="mt-2" id="contact-form" action="#" method="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Full Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone Number *</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="company">Company Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="company" name="company" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="revenue">Annual Revenue Range</label>
            <select id="revenue" name="revenue">
              <option value="">Select range</option>
              <option value="under-5m">Under $5M</option>
              <option value="5m-20m">$5M - $20M</option>
              <option value="20m-50m">$20M - $50M</option>
              <option value="50m-100m">$50M - $100M</option>
              <option value="100m-plus">$100M+</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="service">Service Interest</label>
            <select id="service" name="service">
              <option value="">Select service</option>
              <option value="growth-strategy">Growth Strategy</option>
              <option value="operational-excellence">Operational Excellence</option>
              <option value="market-expansion">Market Expansion</option>
              <option value="digital-transformation">Digital Transformation</option>
              <option value="multiple">Multiple Services</option>
              <option value="unsure">Not Sure Yet</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Tell Us About Your Objectives *</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="What are your primary business objectives? What challenges are you facing?"></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" style="width: 100%;">Submit Request</button>

          <p class="mt-1" style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--medium-gray);">We typically respond within 24 hours. All consultations are confidential.</p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Information -->
      <div>
        <h2>Direct Contact</h2>
        <p>Prefer to reach out directly? Contact us using the information below.</p>

        <div class="card mt-2">
          <h3>Phone</h3>
          <p><a href="tel:{{ site.phone }}" style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600;">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
          <p style="color: var(--medium-gray);">Monday - Friday, 9am - 6pm PST</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt-2">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p><a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600;">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
          <p style="color: var(--medium-gray);">We respond within 24 hours</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt-2">
          <h3>LinkedIn</h3>
          <p><a href="{{ site.socials.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600;">Connect on LinkedIn</a></p>
          <p style="color: var(--medium-gray);">Follow for insights and updates</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt-2">
          <h3>Office</h3>
          <p>{{ site.address.street }}<br>
          {{ site.address.city }}, {{ site.address.state }} {{ site.address.zip }}</p>
          <p style="color: var(--medium-gray); margin-top: 0.5rem;">Serving enterprise clients globally</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-2">
          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <p>During our initial consultation, we'll:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Understand your business objectives and challenges</li>
            <li>Discuss potential engagement approaches</li>
            <li>Share relevant case studies and results</li>
            <li>Provide preliminary recommendations</li>
            <li>Outline next steps if there's a fit</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-1">All consultations are confidential and there's no obligation to engage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What happens during the initial consultation?
          <span class="arrow">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>The initial consultation is a 30-minute conversation to understand your business objectives, discuss challenges, and explore whether Seaena is a good fit for your needs. It's confidential with no obligation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          How quickly can we get started?
          <span class="arrow">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>After our initial consultation and agreement on scope, we typically begin engagements within 2-3 weeks. Timeline depends on our current capacity and your organizational readiness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Do you work with companies outside the US?
          <span class="arrow">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. We work with enterprise clients globally. Our engagements are primarily conducted remotely with strategic in-person sessions as needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What size companies do you work with?
          <span class="arrow">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We primarily work with companies that have achieved product-market fit and are ready to scale, typically with $5M+ in annual revenue. Our methodologies are designed for enterprise and high-growth companies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

